          "title": "<i class='fas fa-blind'></i> Have a walk in the historic center"
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "text": " Here you will find 7 churches from different confessions, the gold miner's houses, and other patrimony buildings built by different nations who came here for the gold rush."
          },
          {
            "text": "<br><i class='fas fa-star'></i> <b>How to visit?</b>"
